  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "AI 智能体说今天不下雨，你敢不带伞吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 4.416,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.19,
      "spokenEnd": 3.612,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 的研究发现，如果训练和评测只奖励答对，猜一个答案往往比诚实说不知道更容易得分。",
      "gapBefore": 1.2,
      "audioDuration": 8.664,
      "audioStart": 4.613,
      "spokenStart": 4.812,
      "spokenEnd": 12.482,
      "actualGapBefore": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "早上七点半，智能体让你放心出门。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.744,
      "audioStart": 12.805,
      "spokenStart": 12.982,
      "spokenEnd": 15.776,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "下午你被一场大雨淋透，晚上才知道：它根本没查天气，只是根据最近的趋势猜了一次。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.92,
      "audioStart": 15.84,
      "spokenStart": 16.026,
      "spokenEnd": 22.978,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这期我们就跟着这把伞，学会判断 AI 答案的三道门：这件事现在能不能知道，它凭什么知道，以及如果错了能不能行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 10.608,
      "audioStart": 23.284,
      "spokenStart": 23.478,
      "spokenEnd": 33.122,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "学完后，你能用三道门快速判断一份答案是可以采用、需要核验，还是必须停止。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.776,
      "audioStart": 33.445,
      "spokenStart": 33.622,
      "spokenEnd": 40.444,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这套方法是把研究结论整理成日常判断法。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.56,
      "audioStart": 40.508,
      "spokenStart": 40.694,
      "spokenEnd": 44.29,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.064,
      "audioStart": 44.608,
      "spokenStart": 44.79,
      "spokenEnd": 51.876,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "好，我们把镜头倒回它说“不用带伞”的那一秒。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 4.176,
      "audioStart": 52.502,
      "spokenStart": 52.676,
      "spokenEnd": 55.887,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "语言模型产生答案时，并不是从一个写着“今天天气”的抽屉里取出事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.36,
      "audioStart": 56.202,
      "spokenStart": 56.387,
      "spokenEnd": 61.77,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它更像是在判断：根据眼前这些文字，下一句怎样说最合理。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.664,
      "audioStart": 61.832,
      "spokenStart": 62.02,
      "spokenEnd": 66.705,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这也解释了什么叫幻觉。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.928,
      "audioStart": 66.771,
      "spokenStart": 66.955,
      "spokenEnd": 68.911,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u04",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "幻觉不是语句奇怪，也不只是偶尔口误，而是模型用非常合理的表达，给出了一个可以核对、但实际错误的事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.792,
      "audioStart": 68.963,
      "spokenStart": 69.161,
      "spokenEnd": 77.985,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "模型在预训练中学到的，主要是文字和事实通常怎样一起出现。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.928,
      "audioStart": 78.299,
      "spokenStart": 78.485,
      "spokenEnd": 83.445,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它不会在读到每句话时，都同时得到一张可靠的真假标签。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.52,
      "audioStart": 83.507,
      "spokenStart": 83.695,
      "spokenEnd": 88.242,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "像“水在零摄氏度附近结冰”这种高频而稳定的知识，语言里有大量重复线索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.696,
      "audioStart": 88.306,
      "spokenStart": 88.492,
      "spokenEnd": 94.231,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u04",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "可是“你家附近今天下午四点会不会下雨”，既具体又随时变化，无法靠过去的语言规律补回当前真相。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.072,
      "audioStart": 94.292,
      "spokenStart": 94.481,
      "spokenEnd": 102.58,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "所以模型能够把一句话说得很像答案，不代表它已经观察到了答案所依赖的事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.272,
      "audioStart": 102.91,
      "spokenStart": 103.08,
      "spokenEnd": 109.405,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "生成能力和事实获取能力，是两件不同的事。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.656,
      "audioStart": 109.474,
      "spokenStart": 109.655,
      "spokenEnd": 113.358,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "后训练和评测本来应该减少错误，但如果规则只看答对率，猜测仍然可能得到奖励。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.752,
      "audioStart": 113.678,
      "spokenStart": 113.858,
      "spokenEnd": 120.636,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这就像做一道不会的选择题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.952,
      "audioStart": 120.7,
      "spokenStart": 120.886,
      "spokenEnd": 122.865,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "空着一定不得分，随便选一个却还有猜中的机会。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.896,
      "audioStart": 122.924,
      "spokenStart": 123.115,
      "spokenEnd": 127.023,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "猜一个人的生日，有三百六十五分之一的机会碰巧答对；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.136,
      "audioStart": 127.353,
      "spokenStart": 127.523,
      "spokenEnd": 131.701,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "直接说不知道，却肯定拿不到准确率的分数。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 131.755,
      "spokenStart": 131.951,
      "spokenEnd": 135.26,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "系统如果只奖励命中，就可能慢慢学会：先给答案，别轻易承认未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.6,
      "audioStart": 135.33,
      "spokenStart": 135.51,
      "spokenEnd": 141.151,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 在研究中引用了 SimpleQA。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 141.454,
      "spokenStart": 141.651,
      "spokenEnd": 144.701,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "SimpleQA 是一套事实问答评测，主要由答案明确、可以核对的短问题组成。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.696,
      "audioStart": 144.783,
      "spokenStart": 144.951,
      "spokenEnd": 150.69,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "正因为答案能够验证，它很适合观察模型遇到事实问题时，是答对、猜错，还是选择不回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.64,
      "audioStart": 150.753,
      "spokenStart": 150.94,
      "spokenEnd": 158.613,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "其中一个模型答对百分之二十二，答错百分之二十六，其余问题选择不回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.08,
      "audioStart": 158.938,
      "spokenStart": 159.113,
      "spokenEnd": 165.241,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "另一个模型答对百分之二十四，看起来只高了两点；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 165.3,
      "spokenStart": 165.491,
      "spokenEnd": 169.468,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "但它答错了百分之七十五，而且几乎从不拒答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.632,
      "audioStart": 169.531,
      "spokenStart": 169.718,
      "spokenEnd": 173.395,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果只看答对率，第二个模型似乎稍强。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 173.716,
      "spokenStart": 173.895,
      "spokenEnd": 177.219,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "把错误率和拒答率一起看，你才会发现：它不是知道得更多，而是更愿意猜。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.056,
      "audioStart": 177.286,
      "spokenStart": 177.469,
      "spokenEnd": 183.569,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这带来第一个重要认知：可靠性不是一个准确率数字。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.896,
      "audioStart": 183.633,
      "spokenStart": 183.819,
      "spokenEnd": 187.741,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u04",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "它至少同时包含答对、答错和知道何时不该回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.088,
      "audioStart": 187.809,
      "spokenStart": 187.991,
      "spokenEnd": 192.116,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "因此，面对一份流畅答案，先不要把它当作结论。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.776,
      "audioStart": 192.432,
      "spokenStart": 192.616,
      "spokenEnd": 196.431,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "把它当作一条等待检查的判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.336,
      "audioStart": 196.496,
      "spokenStart": 196.681,
      "spokenEnd": 199.056,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "当你完成这个转换，接下来的问题就很清楚了：这条判断在当前条件下，到底有没有可能被知道？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.088,
      "audioStart": 199.121,
      "spokenStart": 199.306,
      "spokenEnd": 206.417,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二天早上，你又问：我今天出门要带伞吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 4.416,
      "audioStart": 207.031,
      "spokenStart": 207.217,
      "spokenEnd": 210.654,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一次，智能体没有立刻回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.216,
      "audioStart": 210.715,
      "spokenStart": 210.904,
      "spokenEnd": 213.146,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "它先确认你在上海，早上八点出门、晚上七点回来，中间还需要步行。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.48,
      "audioStart": 213.208,
      "spokenStart": 213.396,
      "spokenEnd": 218.911,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u04",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "它还要确认一件更关键的事：自己能不能查询实时天气。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.232,
      "audioStart": 218.983,
      "spokenStart": 219.161,
      "spokenEnd": 223.422,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这些问题共同组成第一道门——可答门。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.936,
      "audioStart": 223.744,
      "spokenStart": 223.922,
      "spokenEnd": 226.891,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它检查的不是模型够不够聪明，而是当前条件是否允许任何人得到可靠答案。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.68,
      "audioStart": 226.955,
      "spokenStart": 227.141,
      "spokenEnd": 233.829,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "一件事可能因为四种原因暂时不可答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.08,
      "audioStart": 234.146,
      "spokenStart": 234.329,
      "spokenEnd": 237.44,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "问题本身不够具体，例如没有地点和时间；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.344,
      "audioStart": 237.5,
      "spokenStart": 237.69,
      "spokenEnd": 241.045,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "所需信息根本拿不到，例如没有天气接口权限；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.752,
      "audioStart": 241.108,
      "spokenStart": 241.295,
      "spokenEnd": 245.07,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u04",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "手里的信息已经过期，例如只有昨天的预报；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.392,
      "audioStart": 245.137,
      "spokenStart": 245.32,
      "spokenEnd": 248.755,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u05",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "或者问题本来就没有唯一答案，例如步行和开车的人对“要不要带伞”有不同标准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.96,
      "audioStart": 248.805,
      "spokenStart": 249.005,
      "spokenEnd": 254.977,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这四种情况都不能靠“再认真推理一次”解决。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 255.289,
      "spokenStart": 255.477,
      "spokenEnd": 258.797,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "推理可以整理已有信息，却不能凭空制造缺失的观察、权限和事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.192,
      "audioStart": 258.868,
      "spokenStart": 259.047,
      "spokenEnd": 264.282,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这就是可答门带来的能力：你能够区分一件事是难以推理，还是在当前信息下根本无法可靠回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.76,
      "audioStart": 264.347,
      "spokenStart": 264.532,
      "spokenEnd": 272.324,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果智能体没有天气查询能力，正确回答不是“我大概有百分之六十把握不下雨”，而是：我无法确认当前天气，最近的趋势只能作为推断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 12.24,
      "audioStart": 272.64,
      "spokenStart": 272.824,
      "spokenEnd": 284.085,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "不确定性也不是把语气改成“可能、也许、大概”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.776,
      "audioStart": 284.15,
      "spokenStart": 284.335,
      "spokenEnd": 288.131,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "真正有用的不确定性，要说明证据处在什么状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.68,
      "audioStart": 288.19,
      "spokenStart": 288.381,
      "spokenEnd": 292.09,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "已经查到并且能够对应证据的，是已确认事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.704,
      "audioStart": 292.4,
      "spokenStart": 292.59,
      "spokenEnd": 296.33,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "有一些支持，但证据还没有覆盖全部条件的，是有支持但不完整。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.36,
      "audioStart": 296.395,
      "spokenStart": 296.58,
      "spokenEnd": 301.968,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "根据事实和假设进一步得出的，是推断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.08,
      "audioStart": 302.031,
      "spokenStart": 302.218,
      "spokenEnd": 305.32,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u04",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "当前缺少信息、工具或唯一答案的，是未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.8,
      "audioStart": 305.384,
      "spokenStart": 305.57,
      "spokenEnd": 309.418,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "放回带伞的故事里，你的位置和出行时间已经确认；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.992,
      "audioStart": 309.739,
      "spokenStart": 309.918,
      "spokenEnd": 313.941,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这个季节容易出现阵雨，只是一种推断；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.864,
      "audioStart": 314.004,
      "spokenStart": 314.191,
      "spokenEnd": 317.082,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "今天几点下雨，在查询之前仍然是未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.44,
      "audioStart": 317.157,
      "spokenStart": 317.332,
      "spokenEnd": 320.804,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这四种状态比“百分之八十七可信”更有价值。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.416,
      "audioStart": 321.119,
      "spokenStart": 321.304,
      "spokenEnd": 324.748,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "除非系统针对这类任务做过真正的校准，否则精确百分比只会让证据缺口看起来更科学。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.28,
      "audioStart": 324.813,
      "spokenStart": 324.998,
      "spokenEnd": 332.309,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "通过可答门以后，你已经知道这件事能不能回答，也知道哪些部分还不能回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.96,
      "audioStart": 332.632,
      "spokenStart": 332.809,
      "spokenEnd": 338.824,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "但“能够查到”仍然不等于“现有证据已经足够”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.008,
      "audioStart": 339.129,
      "spokenStart": 339.324,
      "spokenEnd": 342.35,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "你还需要第二道门：它到底凭什么知道？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.84,
      "audioStart": 342.406,
      "spokenStart": 342.6,
      "spokenEnd": 345.465,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "智能体打开当地气象部门的最新预报。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 3.84,
      "audioStart": 346.075,
      "spokenStart": 346.265,
      "spokenEnd": 349.121,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "假设预报提示下午可能有阵雨，它又查看临近降雨和雷达信息，确认云雨带是否接近你的活动区域。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.048,
      "audioStart": 349.192,
      "spokenStart": 349.371,
      "spokenEnd": 357.442,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这就是第二道门——证据门。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.856,
      "audioStart": 357.498,
      "spokenStart": 357.692,
      "spokenEnd": 359.581,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "证据门不只检查有没有来源，还要检查三个更重要的问题：来源离事实有多近，不同来源是否真的独立，以及证据究竟支持了哪一句判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 11.664,
      "audioStart": 359.892,
      "spokenStart": 360.081,
      "spokenEnd": 370.772,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "天气预报直接来自气象部门，比一篇转述天气的文章更靠近事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.192,
      "audioStart": 371.092,
      "spokenStart": 371.272,
      "spokenEnd": 376.497,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "最新雷达提供了另一个观察角度，可以帮助判断预报中的降雨是否正在接近。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.96,
      "audioStart": 376.571,
      "spokenStart": 376.747,
      "spokenEnd": 382.742,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "三个应用写着同一句话，不一定是三份独立证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.68,
      "audioStart": 383.072,
      "spokenStart": 383.242,
      "spokenEnd": 386.96,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它们可能只是复制了同一个数据源。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.312,
      "audioStart": 387.022,
      "spokenStart": 387.21,
      "spokenEnd": 389.545,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "来源数量增加了，信息却没有增加。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.72,
      "audioStart": 389.611,
      "spokenStart": 389.795,
      "spokenEnd": 392.552,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "同样，预报说“上海下午有阵雨”，不等于你所在的街道四点整必然下雨。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.504,
      "audioStart": 392.864,
      "spokenStart": 393.052,
      "spokenEnd": 398.577,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "雷达看到云带接近，也不等于它一定会在你走出地铁站时落雨。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.144,
      "audioStart": 398.631,
      "spokenStart": 398.827,
      "spokenEnd": 403.98,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "证据支持到哪里，判断就说到哪里。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.456,
      "audioStart": 404.034,
      "spokenStart": 404.23,
      "spokenEnd": 406.709,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "这叫判断和证据对齐。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.64,
      "audioStart": 406.771,
      "spokenStart": 406.959,
      "spokenEnd": 408.628,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u05",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "很多自信错误并不是引用了假信息，而是把真实信息贴到了错误日期、错误地区、错误对象或错误条件上。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.96,
      "audioStart": 408.7,
      "spokenStart": 408.878,
      "spokenEnd": 417.876,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u06",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 5,
      "text": "证据门要做的，就是阻止结论悄悄超出证据范围。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.872,
      "audioStart": 417.932,
      "spokenStart": 418.126,
      "spokenEnd": 422.016,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在，智能体可以说：你今天在上海，八点到十九点之间需要步行。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.552,
      "audioStart": 422.332,
      "spokenStart": 422.516,
      "spokenEnd": 428.097,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "最新预报提示下午可能有阵雨，雷达也显示云雨带正在接近。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.904,
      "audioStart": 428.187,
      "spokenStart": 428.347,
      "spokenEnd": 433.311,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "现在不能确认你一定会淋到雨，但带一把折叠伞的成本很低，我建议带上。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.816,
      "audioStart": 433.383,
      "spokenStart": 433.561,
      "spokenEnd": 439.42,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这份回答仍然承认未知，却已经足够支持一个低成本的决定。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.736,
      "audioStart": 439.731,
      "spokenStart": 439.92,
      "spokenEnd": 444.672,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "于是我们来到第三道门——行动门。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.624,
      "audioStart": 444.737,
      "spokenStart": 444.922,
      "spokenEnd": 447.581,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "行动门不再问答案像不像真的，而是问：如果判断错了，损失有多大；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.6,
      "audioStart": 447.911,
      "spokenStart": 448.081,
      "spokenEnd": 453.725,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "已经执行以后，能不能轻易撤销。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.384,
      "audioStart": 453.789,
      "spokenStart": 453.975,
      "spokenEnd": 456.394,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "多带一把伞，最多增加一点重量，所以证据不完美时，可以选择更稳妥的做法。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.32,
      "audioStart": 456.452,
      "spokenStart": 456.644,
      "spokenEnd": 463,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果同样的不确定判断会触发转账、用药、修改权限或公开发布，门槛就必须提高。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.184,
      "audioStart": 463.312,
      "spokenStart": 463.5,
      "spokenEnd": 470.734,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体可以查资料、整理证据和提出建议，但在高影响、难撤销的行动前，必须停下来等待人工确认。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.36,
      "audioStart": 470.79,
      "spokenStart": 470.984,
      "spokenEnd": 479.362,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "这不是对所有任务都进行同样复杂的核验，而是让核验成本跟随错误后果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.984,
      "audioStart": 479.423,
      "spokenStart": 479.612,
      "spokenEnd": 485.618,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "低风险任务可以快速检查，高风险任务需要一手证据、独立核验和明确批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.608,
      "audioStart": 485.683,
      "spokenStart": 485.868,
      "spokenEnd": 492.501,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在，把三道门展开，就得到完整的六步事实核验清单。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.496,
      "audioStart": 492.817,
      "spokenStart": 493.001,
      "spokenEnd": 497.536,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "可答门负责写清问题和关键判断；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 497.597,
      "spokenStart": 497.786,
      "spokenEnd": 500.412,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "证据门负责定义证据标准并完成真实核验；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.416,
      "audioStart": 500.476,
      "spokenStart": 500.662,
      "spokenEnd": 504.1,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "行动门负责评估风险，并把失败保存成新的测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 504.174,
      "spokenStart": 504.35,
      "spokenEnd": 508.334,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u05",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "这六步对应的是：可答性、判断清单、证据标准、真实核验、行动风险和反馈测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.376,
      "audioStart": 508.395,
      "spokenStart": 508.584,
      "spokenEnd": 515.98,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二天，如果预报和实际天气不一致，记录当时的问题、证据和结果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.576,
      "audioStart": 516.285,
      "spokenStart": 516.48,
      "spokenEnd": 522.062,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "下一次再遇到相同情况，系统就能检查自己是否又犯了同一种错误。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.36,
      "audioStart": 522.129,
      "spokenStart": 522.312,
      "spokenEnd": 527.702,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "到这里，AI 给出的已经不只是一句答案，而是一条可以检查的决策链：问题是什么，证据在哪里，哪些仍然未知，以及下一步允许做什么。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 11.784,
      "audioStart": 528.014,
      "spokenStart": 528.202,
      "spokenEnd": 539,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在，把两次回答放在一起看。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 3.288,
      "audioStart": 539.616,
      "spokenStart": 539.8,
      "spokenEnd": 542.13,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一次，智能体只说：不用带伞，今天是晴天。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.848,
      "audioStart": 542.199,
      "spokenStart": 542.38,
      "spokenEnd": 546.255,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "它很短、很顺、很自信，却没有告诉你它根本没查。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.232,
      "audioStart": 546.327,
      "spokenStart": 546.505,
      "spokenEnd": 550.774,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u04",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "第二次，它先判断问题是否可答，再核对来源和证据范围，最后根据错误后果给出一个容易撤销的行动建议。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.552,
      "audioStart": 550.833,
      "spokenStart": 551.024,
      "spokenEnd": 559.592,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u05",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "第二个答案不一定更像一个无所不知的 AI，但它更像一个值得信任的助手。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.36,
      "audioStart": 559.651,
      "spokenStart": 559.842,
      "spokenEnd": 565.226,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "更重要的是，你已经获得了一项可以迁移到任何 AI 任务的能力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.832,
      "audioStart": 565.538,
      "spokenStart": 565.726,
      "spokenEnd": 570.608,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "看到确定答案时，先过可答门：这件事现在真的能够知道吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.048,
      "audioStart": 570.671,
      "spokenStart": 570.858,
      "spokenEnd": 575.946,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "再过证据门：它凭什么知道，证据是否支持它说的全部内容？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.76,
      "audioStart": 576.023,
      "spokenStart": 576.196,
      "spokenEnd": 580.999,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u04",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "最后过行动门：如果判断错了，损失是什么，这个动作还能不能撤销？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.624,
      "audioStart": 581.072,
      "spokenStart": 581.249,
      "spokenEnd": 586.921,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "三道门都通过，答案才有资格进入行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.032,
      "audioStart": 587.25,
      "spokenStart": 587.421,
      "spokenEnd": 590.497,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "任何一道门失败，就去补信息、重新核验、请求人工批准，或者停止。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.744,
      "audioStart": 590.563,
      "spokenStart": 590.747,
      "spokenEnd": 596.52,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "以后你不需要先判断模型到底有多聪明。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.152,
      "audioStart": 596.583,
      "spokenStart": 596.77,
      "spokenEnd": 599.957,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u04",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "只要沿着这三道门，就能把“它说得很像真的”，转换成“这份答案是否足以支持我的决定”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.392,
      "audioStart": 600.021,
      "spokenStart": 600.207,
      "spokenEnd": 606.645,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "目标不是让 AI 智能体变得胆小，也不是让每个答案都拖得很长。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.784,
      "audioStart": 606.957,
      "spokenStart": 607.145,
      "spokenEnd": 611.945,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "目标是让它的每一份自信，都先说明依据，再获得影响现实的资格。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.096,
      "audioStart": 612.001,
      "spokenStart": 612.195,
      "spokenEnd": 617.321,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "关注 Tiny Agent，成为更擅长使用 AI 的人！",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 617.628,
      "spokenStart": 617.821,
      "spokenEnd": 620.887,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    }
  ],
